additional_info:
Blurry image courtesy of Userstyles' 100kb limit on screenshots. They don't do it justice, see firsthand instead of relying on them.

After downloading, add this line to the top of the theme (after removing the %s) to use the font intended.
@import "http%:%//fonts%.%googleapis%.%com/%css?family=Molengo";


Credit to the cutie mark vector goes to Inixen from DeviantArt, it really ties the design together.

css:
@-moz-document domain('ponychan.net') {
body {
	background: #2E1D47 !important;
	background-image:url("http://img694.imageshack.us/img694/3447/60078.png") !important;
	background-repeat:no-repeat !important;
	background-attachment:fixed !important;
	background-position: bottom right !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	text-shadow: 1px 1px #000000 !important;

} 
.logo { 
	color: #457AC5 !important;
	text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000 !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	font-size:400% !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#verytopbar, #themedropdown, #watchedthreads {
	-moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px !important;
	box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px !important;
	-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px !important;
}
#sitesidebar .menuexpander {
	color: #314D7E !important;
}
#verytopbar h1 {
	color: #457AC5 !important;
	text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000 !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	font-size:400% !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

#verytopbar h3 { 
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-size: 0px !important;
}

#verytopbar h3:after { 
	display: block !important;
	font-style: italic !important;
	font-size: 24px !important;
	content: '"The Shadowbolts were here, the Blunderbolts are losers."' !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
}
h3:after { 
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	display: block !important;
	font-style: italic !important;
	font-size: 24px !important;
	content: '"The Shadowbolts were here, the Blunderbolts are losers."' !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
}
a, a:visited{
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
a:hover, a:active, .reflink a:hover {
	font-weight: normal !important;
	color: #D4D197 !important;
}


#verytopbar, .adminbar, #themedropdown {
	background: #221535 !important;
	box-shadow: 3px 3px 8px #2E1D47 !important;
	-moz-box-shadow: 3px 3px 8px #2E1D47 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;

}
hr{
	background-color: #B4B280 !important;
	height: 1px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

#verytopbar a {
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	border-top-color: #314D7E !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#verytopbar a:hover {
	background: #2A2C55 !important;
	color: #D4D197 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#verytopbar a:hover, #verytopbar .navbarcurboard {
	border-top-color: #939BCB !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

#sitesidebar a:hover, #topmenu li {
	background: #D8D8F0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#sitesidebar h2, .newsentry h2, #topmenu li.current {
	background: #C0C0F0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;

}

.postblock {
	background: #314D7E !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.postarea input[type=text], .postarea input[type=password], .postarea textarea {
	border-color: #90A0D0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.postarea input[type=text]:focus, .postarea input[type=password]:focus, .postarea textarea:focus {
	border-color: #0020C0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.postarea{
	padding-top: 10px !important;
	margin-bottom: 10px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.postarea table{
	border-spacing: 0px !important;
	border-collapse: collapse !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

.helphover div, .reply, .highlight, .reflinkpreview {
	background: #21173A !important;
	padding: 0px 5px !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	border-radius: 9px !important; 
	border-color: #314D7E !important; 
	border-width: 2px !important; 
	border-style: solid !important; 
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.highlight, .reflinkpreview {
	border-left-color: #4060b0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

.filetitle {
	color: #c9c6e9 !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.postername, .postername a, .postertrip, .posttime, .reflink {
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	border-bottom-color: #6080e0 !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;

}
.userdelete {
	padding-right:175px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#watchedthreadsdraghandle {
	border-radius: 9px !important;
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	padding-bottom: -5px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

#sitemiddle .newsentry {
	background: #21173A !important;
	padding: 0px 5px !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	border-radius: 9px !important; 
	border-color: #314D7E !important; 
	border-width: 2px !important; 
	border-style: solid !important; 
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
#sitemiddle .newsentry a {
	background: #21173A !important;
	padding: 0px 5px !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	border-radius: 9px !important; 
	border-color: #314D7E !important; 
	border-width: 2px !important; 
	border-style: solid !important; 
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}

#sitesidebar a:hover, #topmenu li {
	background: #314D7E !important;
	color: #4070C0 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.newsentry h2, .newssubtitle {
	background: #21173A !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.recentpostitem, #sitesidebar h2, #topmenu li.current {
	background: #21173A !important;
	padding: 0px 5px !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	border-radius: 9px !important; 
	border-color: #314D7E !important; 
	border-width: 2px !important; 
	border-style: solid !important; 
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.filesize, .newstimestamp {
	color: #4070C0 !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.unkfunc, .omittedposts {
	color: #D4D197 !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
div.thread {
	color: #FFFFFF !important;
}
#topmenu li.tab {
	background: #2A2C55 !important;
	padding: 0px 5px !important;
	color: #C6D5EA !important;
	font-family: 'Molengo' !important; 
	border-radius: 9px !important; 
	border-color: #314D7E !important; 
	border-width: 2px !important; 
	border-style: solid !important; 
	-moz-border-radius: 9px !important;
	font-weight: normal !important;
}
.spoiler {
	background-color: #314D7E !important;
	color: #314D7E !important;
	text-shadow: 0px 0px transparent !important;
}
.spoiler:hover { 
	background-color: transparent !important;
	color: #FFFFFF !important;
	text-shadow: 1px 1px #000000 !important;
}}
